%83n-T%C3%B4ng/author-J50Vl67kW8hllkOChILyMA">Nguyễn Hiển Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-K%E1%BB%B3-kh%C3%AD/poem-CG2qhJF0z8Lnj6wrDzFSmQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Kỳ khí” - 奉和御製奇氣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/author-7XXX3GnZ0T6el9FCsBAeug">Ngô Hoán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90inh-Nghi-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C3%A1n/poem-YCfEXaT3BLx57_5YFKwluQ">Tặng Đinh Nghi, Vương Xán - 贈丁儀王粲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/Tu%E1%BA%BF-m%E1%BB%99-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-27Hcu_V4qJ1M8tV9qyhKpg">Tuế mộ cảm hoài - 歲暮感懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-gsSbrX8mxDOHV8mbduxYMg">Vương Vũ Xứng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-th%E1%BA%BF-ch%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-pwYVzZ3mpuX7PHg6BRMRqA">Việt Nam thế chí tự - 越南世志序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
